title: We messed up
description: We made a grave mistake that resulted in no guest today. We go over that along with a recap of Drake vs Fantano, a part 2 of our HR segment with beefs between Zach and Ethan/Hila, we talk Nick Cannon's growing family, a beef with Dad, and much more!
